{"id":"int-1420b657","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-07-03T06:35:57.737307522Z","actor":"Nick Williams","issue_id":"prexu-axj4.4","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Engine selection/fallback/Settings toggle shipped in PR #31; controls auto-hide hardware-verified; attribution logging kept permanently with mousemove re-arm demoted to trace (PR #32)"}}
{"id":"int-240be1e7","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-07-03T22:14:37.225074224Z","actor":"Nick Williams","issue_id":"prexu-3iv3","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"open","reason":"Fixed and verified on hardware 2026-07-03: two root causes — (1) detach_mpv freed the mpv render context without gl_area.make_current(), corrupting GDK's GL/compositing state (window stopped committing buffers → frozen on last frame, black after resize); (2) card-enter 'both' fill kept finished transform animations permanently active on every poster card, livelocking webkit2gtk 2.52 in CSS transition retargeting on any document-wide class flip. User verified two consecutive play->stop cycles (button + Esc) with no freeze."}}
{"id":"int-dbeb6564","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-07-03T22:56:20.521766116Z","actor":"Nick Williams","issue_id":"prexu-skr2","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"open","reason":"Fixed and verified on hardware 2026-07-03: circular render/vo deadlock in mpv's block-for-target-time wait, triggered by exit_minimize's video-margin-ratio writes mid-playback. Fix: vendored libmpv2 4.1.0 adding RenderContext::render_no_block (BLOCK_FOR_TARGET_TIME=0), used by the Linux compositor render handler; plus busy/ready parity on Linux exit_minimize. User verified: expand restores immediately, video stays live; M7 (stop while mini -> replay full-frame) and M8 (fullscreen interplay after minimize) both pass. Remaining visual staging tracked in prexu-hg1j."}}
{"id":"int-fdcd73f2","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-07-04T17:13:12.885056124Z","actor":"Nick Williams","issue_id":"prexu-91t8","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Fixed in PR #36 (main 46de2d3): host-window-ready now emitted from the GLArea render handler on the first rendered frame per load (armed at first PlaybackRestart, disarmed on FileLoaded/detach). On-hardware verify steps recorded in issue comment / axj4.5 test plan."}}
{"id":"int-75eb6902","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-07-04T17:29:40.634603319Z","actor":"Nick Williams","issue_id":"prexu-91k4","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Fixed in PR #37: sub-scale set to mini video height fraction + sub-use-margins=no in apply_margin_ratios (single choke point for enter/update/exit/resize-while-mini); zero ratios restore defaults. On-hardware verify: subs in mini mode should render proportionally small inside the mini rect."}}
